import math

def calculate_total_signing_time(n, k, coordinates):
    total_distance = 1
    for i in range(1, n):
        (x1, y1) = coordinates[i - 1]
        (x2, y2) = coordinates[i]
        distance = math.sqrt((x2 - x1) ** 2 + (y2 - y1) ** 2)
        total_distance += distance
    total_time = total_distance * k / 50
    return total_time
